def g(c):
    def f(t):
        return 1-exp(-c*t) - t
    return f
x = fsolve(g(2),2)
print("The solution is {:.5f}".format(x[0]))

c = arange(0,3,0.01)
x =[]
for i in c:
    x.append(fsolve(g(i),1))

plot(c,x)
ylabel("x")
xlabel("c")
show()
